nodes.text: Dellis Yuls was a male Quarren. He was Chief of Security for Ororo Transportation, the main rival of the Falleen crime lord Prince Xizor's cargo company. Xizor would later send the Human replica droid, Guri, to attack the main facility.[source?] She twisted Yuls's neck until it snapped, and then shot him in the back to verify his demise.
